import React from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Grid,
  Text,
  Flex,
  Accordion,
  rem,
  Center,
  Avatar,
} from "@mantine/core";
import ResponsivePhone from "./ResponsivePhone";
const Home = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Box
        h={40}
        w={`100%`}
        bg="gray.2"
        mt="xs"
        gap="md"
        justify="center"
        align="center"
      >
        <Text>Home</Text>
        <Text></Text>
        <Text></Text>
        <Text></Text>
      </Box>
      <Grid>
        <Grid.Col span={4}>
          <Box m="xs" bg="gray.2">
            <Flex
              mih={50}
              mt="xs"
              bg="indigo.5"
              gap="md"
              justify="center"
              align="center"
              direction="row"
              wrap="wrap"
            >
              <Text>Layout</Text>
            </Flex>
            <Accordion m="xs" variant="contained">
              <Accordion.Item value="photos">
                <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
                  <Center>Slider</Center>
                </Accordion.Control>
                <Accordion.Panel>Content</Accordion.Panel>
              </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
            <Accordion m="xs" variant="contained">
              <Accordion.Item value="photos">
                <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
                  <Center>Category List</Center>
                </Accordion.Control>
                <Accordion.Panel>
                  <Box>
                    <Avatar
                      variant="filled"
                      radius="sm"
                      size="lg"
                      color="yellow"
                      src="https://blogassets.leverageedu.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/02232228/BSc-Electronics.png"
                    />
                    <Text size="xs">Electronics</Text>
                    <Avatar variant="filled" radius="sm" size="lg" color="grape" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRXRklc2x3ukmoEmuGbD36aOWy2gVwDP_1yUg&usqp=CAU" />
                  </Box>
                </Accordion.Panel>
              </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
            <Accordion m="xs" variant="contained">
              <Accordion.Item value="photos">
                <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
                  <Center>Category With Product</Center>
                </Accordion.Control>
                <Accordion.Panel>Content</Accordion.Panel>
              </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
            <Accordion m="xs" variant="contained">
              <Accordion.Item value="photos">
                <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
                  <Center>Brand List</Center>
                </Accordion.Control>
                <Accordion.Panel>Content</Accordion.Panel>
              </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
            <Accordion m="xs" variant="contained">
              <Accordion.Item value="photos">
                <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
                  <Center>Brand With Product</Center>
                </Accordion.Control>
                <Accordion.Panel>Content</Accordion.Panel>
              </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
            <Accordion m="xs" variant="contained">
              <Accordion.Item value="photos">
                <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
                  <Center>Latest Product/ Recently Added</Center>
                </Accordion.Control>
                <Accordion.Panel>Content</Accordion.Panel>
              </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
            <Accordion m="xs" variant="contained">
              <Accordion.Item value="photos">
                <Accordion.Control bg="indigo.2">
                  <Center>Most Populer Product</Center>
                </Accordion.Control>
                <Accordion.Panel>Content</Accordion.Panel>
              </Accordion.Item>
            </Accordion>
          </Box>
        </Grid.Col>
        <Grid.Col span={4} mt="xs">
          <ResponsivePhone />
        </Grid.Col>
        <Grid.Col span={4}>3</Grid.Col>
      </Grid>
    </>
  );
};

export default Home;
